title: Independent candidate Mehboob Sher wins PK-67 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent candidate Mehboob Sher has won the Khyber Pakhtunkhwa Assembly election from PK-67, Mohmand-I by securing 15,127 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Awami National Party (ANP) candidate Nisar Ahmed who bagged 7,413 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 31.14 per cent.
